---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Rift Wars" description="Privacy Policy for Rift Wars by Meta Machina Studio LLC.">
  <section class="section-padding pt-32 bg-mm-bg">
    <div class="section-container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-orbitron text-3xl font-bold text-mm-text mb-8 neon-text">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Meta Machina Studio LLC</strong> ("Company," "we," "us") collects, uses,
          and protects your information when you use Rift Wars and related services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed"><strong>Account Data:</strong> When you create an account via Google OAuth, we receive your display name and email address. When you connect a Solana wallet, we store your public wallet address. We never have access to your private keys or wallet seed phrases.</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed"><strong>Gameplay Data:</strong> Match history, ELO rating, level, XP, card collection, deck configurations, clan membership, friends list, skill allocations, M-Credz balance, and tutorial progress.</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed"><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address (for rate limiting and anti-abuse), browser/device type (from HTTP headers), and WebSocket connection metadata. We do not use Google Analytics or third-party tracking scripts.</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed"><strong>Communications:</strong> In-game direct messages and clan chat messages are stored on our servers to provide the messaging service.</p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Providing the game experience: matchmaking, leaderboards, social features, account management</li>
          <li>Anti-cheat and abuse prevention (IP-based rate limiting, multi-account detection)</li>
          <li>Game balance analysis using aggregated, anonymized gameplay statistics</li>
          <li>Processing transactions (M-Credz, packs, battle passes) when applicable</li>
          <li>Communicating service updates, security notices, or policy changes</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed"><strong>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</strong></p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Google OAuth:</strong> Used for account authentication. Subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Amazon Web Services (AWS):</strong> Our servers, database (Aurora PostgreSQL), and cache (ElastiCache Redis) are hosted in the us-west-2 (Oregon) region.</li>
          <li><strong>Solana Blockchain:</strong> Wallet authentication and future NFT/token transactions occur on a public blockchain. On-chain transactions are publicly visible by nature.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Data is stored on AWS infrastructure in the United States (us-west-2). All data transmission uses HTTPS/TLS 1.2+.
          Database credentials are stored in AWS Secrets Manager. We follow industry-standard security practices including
          CORS restrictions, rate limiting, input validation, and parameterized database queries.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Account data is retained for as long as your account is active. Guest accounts and their data are periodically purged.
          If you request account deletion, we will delete your personal data within 30 days. Anonymized, aggregated gameplay
          statistics may be retained indefinitely for game balance purposes. On-chain data (NFT ownership, blockchain transactions)
          cannot be deleted as it is part of the public blockchain record.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your account and personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request your data in a machine-readable format</li>
          <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain processing activities</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>California Residents (CCPA):</strong> You have the right to know what personal information we collect, request its deletion,
          and opt out of its sale. We do not sell personal information.
        </p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>EEA Residents (GDPR):</strong> You have additional rights under the General Data Protection Regulation, including the
          right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.
        </p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@metamachina.io" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">legal@metamachina.io</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">7. Children</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          The Service is not directed at children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 18.
          If you believe a minor has provided us with personal information, contact us and we will delete it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via the Service or our website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">9. Contact</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Meta Machina Studio LLC<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@metamachina.io" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">legal@metamachina.io</a><br />
          Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/dNcvNkc33C" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">discord.gg/dNcvNkc33C</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
